<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.5.4">
<l>kaṭuvāyc ciṉaveṅ kaṇkaḷiṟ ṟiṉukkuk</l>
<l rend="indent">kavaḷa meṭuttuk koṭuppā ṉavaṉpō</l>
<l>laṭivā yuṟakkai yiṭṭeḻap paṟittiṭ</l>
<l rend="indent">ṭamarar perumāṉ koṇṭuniṉ ṟamalai</l>
<l>kaṭalvāyc ceṉṟumē kaṅkaviḻn tiṟaṅkik</l>
<l rend="indent">katuvāyp paṭanīr mukantē ṟiyeṅkum</l>
<l>kuṭavāyp paṭaniṉ ṟumaḻai poḻiyuṅ</l>
<l rend="indent">kōvart taṉameṉ ṉuṅkoṟṟak kuṭaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The mountain where the Lord of celestials stood,</l>
<l rend="indent">having placed [his] hand</l>
<l rend="indent">in order to grasp the base [and] pluck [it] up</l>
<l rend="indent">as if he picked up and tossed a ball of rice</l>
<l rend="indent">to a gaping mouthed, red-eyed elephant,</l>
<l>called Govardana,</l>
<l rend="indent">where—the clouds moving to the sea, dipping down,</l>
<l rend="indent">sinking in, and drawing up the water everywhere</l>
<l rend="indent">so that it is diminished [from the sea] —</l>
<l rend="indent">the rain flows as if from a water pot,</l>
<l>is [his] victory umbrella!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
